  "text": "These days, automated things such as vehicles, drones, sensors, machines, and robots, combined with artificial intelligence (AI) technologies, have found their way into almost every industry. Remarkable growth of business models using autonomous machines is accelerating the need for communication between machines as well as machine to human communications [CITATION_1] .",
